author: dtroiano99
body:
This is a new AK8 PNet-MD model for new HLT paths at V1.0 2026 pp collision menu (**deadline HLT JIRA Feb-04**). The new Pnet-MD version has been trained to be more independent from pT and soft-drop mass of AK8 jets. Merging this pull request will enable the new paths.

The paths containing the new model have passed the timing and rate studies. 

All details can be found here [1].

[1] https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-3672
title: New AK8 PNet-MD model for HLT
